title: Wind Under My Wings
tags: 2010 Compowinner Demo Euskal Lyrics video Vocals Windows
info:
Soundtrack from winner demo of Euskal 2010.

[i]Lyrics:

I feel,
a minute of confusion
I fear,
the venom of seclusion in my mind

I seal,
a fate no less than perfect
I steal,
the life that someone left in my back yard

Hear the call
Break the wall
Run for it or take the fall

Standing tall
Make the call
Not afraid to lose it all

Always slow
Taste the flow
Never been before so low

But here I lay
Roles I play
Much to everyone's dismay

No more rings
Binding strings
I want the wind under my wings[/i]
